 for the future will mean for the region and the rest of the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aIslamic fundamentalism. 7aRELIGION / Islam / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311066771440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021601140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300216011423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300216011/original  a978-3-11-066771-4  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles